PortSystem 1.0

name            glark
version         1.8.0
platforms       darwin
categories      textproc
maintainers     freebsdcluster.org:mich
description     Search text files for complex regular expressions
long_description \
    A replacement for (or supplement to) the grep family, glark \
    offers: Perl/Ruby regular expressions, highlighting of matches, \
    complex expressions (``and'' and ``or''), and automatic exclusion \
    of non-text files.
homepage        http://www.incava.org/projects/glark/
master_sites    http://www.incava.org/pub/glark/
